<title>msjwn wbạḥlm bạlḥryẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (msjwn wbạḥlm bạlḥryẗ .. bqlb ḥzyn wrạ qḍbạn
 mstny ạlnwr fy lyl mtạ̉lm .. fjrh lʿyny swr wḥyṭạn)2
 ạlqrạr- (lḥd mạ jạny wṣwth ndạny .. qwm ạlywm mạntạsẖ ạ̉syr)2
 ksrt syf ạlsjạn .. wkẖlạṣy ạ̹dyth bạlmjạn
 (ạ̹frd lfwq jnạḥyk .. wftḥ fy ạlnwr ʿynyk)2
 (dh kl mạly hw lyk)2
 2- (kạnt ʿysẖty ạ̉syr lqywdy .. skẗ ṭwylẗ wḥml tqyl
 ḍʿfy mạlyny wmyn ysẖfyny .. wmyn yrḥmny wạnạ ʿlyl)2</lyrics>
